<h1>Blazor Menu Component</h1>

<p>This application demonstrates a multi-level dropdown menu component in Blazor.</p>

<p><a href="menu-example" class="btn btn-primary">View Example Page</a></p>

<h2>Features</h2>
<ul>
    <li><strong>Unlimited Nesting:</strong> Menu items can be nested to any depth</li>
    <li><strong>Position-Aware Submenus:</strong>
        <ul>
            <li>First level submenus appear <strong>below</strong> their parent item</li>
            <li>Deeper level submenus appear to the <strong>right</strong> of their parent</li>
        </ul>
    </li>
    <li><strong>Hover Activation:</strong> Submenus appear when hovering over parent items</li>
    <li><strong>Auto-Hiding:</strong> Submenus automatically hide when mouse moves away</li>
    <li><strong>Visual Indicators:</strong> Arrow symbols indicate items that have submenus</li>
</ul>

<h2>Menu Structure</h2>
<p>The menu component uses a declarative syntax that matches the hierarchical nature of menus:</p>

<pre>
&lt;Menu&gt;
    &lt;MenuItems&gt;
        &lt;MenuItem Text="Item 1"&gt;
            &lt;MenuItems&gt;
                &lt;MenuItem Text="Item 1.1"&gt;&lt;/MenuItem&gt;
                &lt;MenuItem Text="Item 1.2"&gt;
                    &lt;MenuItems&gt;
                        &lt;MenuItem Text="Item 1.2.1"&gt;&lt;/MenuItem&gt;
                        &lt;MenuItem Text="Item 1.2.2"&gt;&lt;/MenuItem&gt;
                    &lt;/MenuItems&gt;
                &lt;/MenuItem&gt;
            &lt;/MenuItems&gt;
        &lt;/MenuItem&gt;
        &lt;MenuItem Text="Item 2"&gt;&lt;/MenuItem&gt;
        &lt;MenuItem Text="Item 3"&gt;&lt;/MenuItem&gt;
    &lt;/MenuItems&gt;
&lt;/Menu&gt;
</pre>

<h2>Try It Out</h2>
<p>The navigation bar at the top of this page uses the menu component. Try hovering over "Item 1" to see:</p>
<ol>
    <li>First-level items "Item 1.1" and "Item 1.2" appear <strong>below</strong> "Item 1"</li>
    <li>When hovering over "Item 1.2", second-level items "Item 1.2.1" and "Item 1.2.2" appear to the <strong>right</strong></li>
</ol>

